---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Still">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-[84px] min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-surface">
    <section class="py-24 flex-grow">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <header class="mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-[60px] font-headline text-primary leading-[1.1] mb-6" style="text-wrap: balance;">Terms of Service</h1>
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.28em] font-label font-semibold text-secondary">Last Updated: May 18, 2026</p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-secondary space-y-12 font-body leading-[1.7] animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-4">1. Acceptance of Operational Parameters</h2>
            <p>
              Welcome to Still Studio. These Terms of Service regulate all digital interaction, informational collection routing, discovery scheduling modules, and creative evaluation frameworks accessed via this domain. Navigating our digital pages or submitting an inquiry via our forms binds you directly to the terms of use listed herein.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-4">2. Digital Evaluation and Scope of Use</h2>
            <p>
              This platform serves as an exhibition and contact mechanism for our specialized digital design services. Submitting logistical specifications through our input portals constitutes an exploratory inquiry and does not obligate Still Studio to allocate production space, reserve calendar dates, or deploy custom technical code. A binding creative agreement is established solely upon the execution of a written contract signed by both parties.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-4">3. Accurate Representation of Logistics</h2>
            <p>
              Users utilizing our interactive inquiry utilities are required to provide authentic, accurate, and current parameters regarding operational contacts, timeline indicators, and geographical destinations. We reserve the absolute right to cancel scheduling requests, reject project processing pipelines, or refuse communication routing if any supplied parameter points to intentionally falsified or automated indexing.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-4">4. Intellectual Property Safeguards</h2>
            <p>
              All visual material, stylistic compositions, photographic arrangements, logo expressions, text copy, font configurations, and core source code deployed across this public domain represent the exclusive intellectual property of Still Studio and our parent engine, Massion Digital. 
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-4 border-error/50 text-[15px] text-on-surface-variant rounded-[2px]">
              Users are strictly blocked from harvesting visual templates, cloning interface layouts, scraping public copywriting structures, or duplicating technical rendering logic for commercial or competing structural implementations.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-4">5. Liability Protections and Service Availability</h2>
            <p>
              While we make every reasonable effort to keep our primary informational hubs accurate and online, our digital platform components are presented on an "as-is" basis. We accept no functional or commercial liability for any digital network blockages, processing delay gaps, browser translation errors, or technical data omissions occurring due to network disruptions, third-party server downtimes, or external provider dropouts.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-headline text-on-surface mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-4">6. Governing Regulations and Modifications</h2>
            <p>
              These terms are constructed, interpreted, and regulated under the operational legal frameworks of our primary operating registration. We maintain the autonomous privilege to update, transform, or append these structural terms at our discretion to match evolving technical capabilities and regulatory requirements. 
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              For explicit clarifications regarding terms of processing or corporate execution properties, contact our studio team directly at <a href="mailto:studio@still-studio.com" class="text-primary hover:underline font-semibold">studio@still-studio.com</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>